T1  - PUBLIC ENTERPRISES AND LABOR MARKET PERFORMANCE*
AU  - Hörner, Johannes
AU  - Ngai, L. Rachel
AU  - Olivetti, Claudia
Y1  - 2007/05/01
PY  - 2007
DA  - 2007/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-2354.2007.00431.x
T2  - International Economic Review
