T1  - CANDIDATE VALENCE: EVIDENCE FROM CONSECUTIVE PRESIDENTIAL ELECTIONS*
AU  - Degan, Arianna
Y1  - 2007/05/01
PY  - 2007
DA  - 2007/05/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-2354.2007.00434.x
T2  - International Economic Review
